Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: Everything Kamala Harris says in her speeches is a lie. Yesterday she got up and started ranting and raving that Donald Trump wants to put a tax on gasoline, food, medication, clothing and everything else, when I’ve never said anything of the kind...Here is the truth: Kamala wants to put massive taxes on American jobs and American industries—I want to CUT taxes on Americans, while putting tariffs on China and other foreign countries to bring our jobs back home to Pennsylvania. A tariff is a tax on a foreign country... there's no tax if they build in PA - it's very simple.
